tty-egpf-monitor (0.3.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Add Ubuntu 22.04 (Jammy) compatibility
  * Fix exit status 127 on systems without CAP_BPF capability
  * Add OS-specific package dependencies (libbpf0 vs libbpf1)
  * Implement automatic OS detection in build and install scripts
  * Add APT repository support with GPG signing
  * Create comprehensive testing framework for multi-Ubuntu support
  * Add detailed Ubuntu compatibility documentation

